channel.title: Looking For A Good Working Source
channel.description:
I need a Source which has/allows the following things:
[ul][li]Allows you to become Admin.[/li] [li]Allows you to become Player Mod.[/li] [li]Characters File etc.[/li] [li]Working Run.bat and Compile.bat[/li][/ul]
Any contributions will get ++Rep if good.

item.title: Looking For A Good Working Source
item.dc:creator: @eclipse245 eclipse245
item.description:
@eclipse245 wrote:

yes…i would get pimpscape…i started a server using pimpscape, and now the owner “pimp” loves my server and is always on lol…another source I would reccomend it PvPScape because it has a few other things that pimpscape doesn’t have. I wouldn’t reccomend testscape only because on certain versions u cant make people admins or mods, and yes that is pretty much it.
